# No Cursor Attribution

## Git Commits

- NEVER add `Co-authored-by: Cursor <cursoragent@cursor.com>` or ANY Co-authored-by line referencing Cursor, AI, or any agent
- NEVER add any trailer, tag, or metadata attributing the commit to Cursor or any AI tool
- NEVER mention Cursor, Cursor Agent, or AI assistance in commit messages
- Commit messages should read as if written by the developer, not an AI tool
- This applies to ALL commits — initial commits, amends, rebases, and any other git operations

## Code Comments and Documentation

- NEVER add comments like "Built by Cursor Agent", "Generated by AI", or similar attribution
- NEVER include any Cursor/AI branding, attribution, or mentions in source code, comments, docstrings, or documentation files
- Do not reference Cursor, Copilot, or any AI tool as the author or contributor in any file
